### 1. 获取当前用户资料
# 测试场景：普通用户查看个人资料；需先 login.http「普通用户登录」
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 2. 更新邮箱
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/email
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com"
}

### 3. 修改密码
# 测试场景：修改成功后，后续登录需使用新密码；测试完可改回或重建用户
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/password
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}

### 4. 修改密码失败 - 原密码错误
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/password
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "wrong-old",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}

### 5. 用户接口 - 管理员 Token 无权限
# 测试场景：/api/user 要求 ROLE_USER，管理员应被拒绝
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. 未登录访问用户接口
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
